title: Ronni Ancona & Co.
overview: Welcome to Ronni's world, where familiar faces - including those of Kate Moss and Pete Doherty - mix with a cast of eccentric new characters. What, you didn't think that's the real Punch and Judy, did you?During this spanking new series, Ronni is joined by a host of talented cohorts, including John Sessions, Dead Ringers' Jan Ravens, Daisy Haggard (Man Stroke Woman) and - yes! - Bill Oddie.Look out for Britain's bitchiest airport security guard, Ronni's "teacher on the verge of a nervous breakdown", and the numerous celebrity clients of infamous dry-out hang-out The Friary Clinic.
